-- First, create a test artist profile
INSERT INTO artist_profiles (userId, stageName, bio, genres, location, avatarUrl, socialLinks, createdAt, updatedAt)
VALUES (
  1,
  'Luna Wave',
  'Independent artist creating dreamy electronic soundscapes. Based in Los Angeles.',
  JSON_ARRAY('Electronic', 'Ambient', 'Chillwave'),
  'Los Angeles, CA',
  'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?w=400',
  JSON_OBJECT('spotify', 'https://spotify.com/artist/lunawave', 'instagram', 'lunawave'),
  NOW(),
  NOW()
);

-- Then create a test track
INSERT INTO bap_tracks (
  artistId,
  title,
  artist,
  genre,
  mood,
  audioUrl,
  artworkUrl,
  duration,
  pricePerStream,
  artistShare,
  platformFee,
  playCount,
  likeCount,
  totalEarnings,
  status,
  releasedAt,
  createdAt,
  updatedAt
)
VALUES (
  (SELECT id FROM artist_profiles WHERE stageName = 'Luna Wave' LIMIT 1),
  'Midnight Dreams',
  'Luna Wave',
  'Electronic',
  'Dreamy',
  'https://www.soundhelix.com/examples/mp3/SoundHelix-Song-1.mp3',
  'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1470225620780-dba8ba36b745?w=800',
  240,
  1,
  90,
  10,
  1247,
  89,
  1122,
  'live',
  NOW(),
  NOW(),
  NOW()
);
